{
  "stem": "6719.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It looked like, uh, in the ceiling, it was-- the ceiling was about, oh, I guess as high as that ceiling here, which is, what?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About two and a half meters, three meters, something like that?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were some, uh-- some, uh, shower heads that were built in down there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a column in the center, a column that had wire around it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's, when be washed it up we found, uh, crystals down there that were-- that were still there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know this-- this was Zyklon B.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, nobody's a smart ass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we-- we do [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know that afterwards, but you didn't know it at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ah, I knew, that what-- what-- not what type, but that gas was involved because while I worked in Kanada, there was a hut down there in Kanada where gas was stored.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this SS man that I-- I-- I-- we found in 1900 and what was it? 1900 and 70-- I think I gave you the date on that thing, K, didn't I?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In 1972, he was brought on trial in Vienna that worked in Kanada.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was the [GERMAN], in other words, the meter reader.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- he received a message to take his truck that had, uh, a red cross on-- on-- on-- on two sides and one on the top, which was one of the small delivery truck-like things.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went to the hut.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had the key.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took out the cans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew it was gas, but we didn't know what it was for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he put it in the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went into-- to the crematoriums down there and did his job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was Franz Wunsch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
